#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Altitude2015_1200 <- which(SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude < 1200)
Altitude2015_1600 <- which(SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude >= 1200 & SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude < 1600)
Altitude2015_2000 <- which(SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude >= 1600 & SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude < 2000)
Altitude2015_2400 <- which(SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude >= 2000 & SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude < 2400)

AltitudeGroup <- rep(NULL, length(SweetpotatoSurvey2015$Altitude))

AltitudeGroup[Altitude2015_1200] <- "ALT1200"
AltitudeGroup[Altitude2015_1600] <- "ALT1600"
AltitudeGroup[Altitude2015_2000] <- "ALT2000"
AltitudeGroup[Altitude2015_2400] <- "ALT2400"

SweetpotatoSurvey2015 <- data.frame(SweetpotatoSurvey2015, AltitudeGroup)
